sentences: Ma olen teadlik sellest, et teda ei tohi raiestada.
Ta arvab, et teda juba tean.
Minu lugu on see, et neid kaks inimest, kes mind teda teha soovivad.
context: 'Teda' refers to knowing or being aware of something. It is used as a verb meaning 'to know', and can also be found in phrases like 'I already know it' (et teda juba tean).
